dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This data set shows the boundaries of public school districts in Snohomish County. It is one of several districts which hold elections and is maintained by the Auditor's Office. District bounaries are registered with the Integrated Land Records (ILR) parcel data set, with some exceptions.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
